::Autofire::

Autofire watches the base getting bigger and bigger on the horizon as he approaches it, the two jets that were attacking it becoming visible.

"Ah, we do get to play after all," he mutters to himself, speeding up toward the two small jets.

"Hold on tight, we're gonna be spinning a bit," Autofire says, a seatbelt securing Firestrike as he speeds up and suddenly drops under the ocean, heading toward the Dark Avion underwater.
